Start server
./bin/start-hbase.sh
Hbase Shell
./bin/hbase shell
status
Creating table
hbase(main):001:0> create 'tableTest', 'familyName1’
List all table 
hbase(main):004:0> list
Put 
hbase(main):005:0> put 'tableTest','keyRow1','familyName1:f1','value1’
Scan whole table
hbase(main):007:0> scan 'tableTest’
Get a row
hbase(main):008:0> get 'tableTest','keyRow1’
Disable a table
hbase(main):009:0> disable 'tableTest’
Delete a table
hbase(main):010:0> drop 'tableTest
Changing the Maximum Number of Cells of a Column Family
alter 't1', NAME ⇒ 'f1', VERSIONS ⇒ 5
alter 'emp', NAME ⇒ 'personal data', VERSIONS ⇒ 5
Setting Read Only
alter 't1', READONLY(option)
